Author: henej
Text: Sometimes I look at their licenses and calculate their BMI from that... kind of fucked up but it’s fine 🙂

Author: sadboimochi
Text: Even never having been outside of a “healthy” bmi range, I’ve always been the heaviest friend in any one of my friend groups. Not to mention also being the ugliest.   I’m not proud of this but this pattern is definitely why I have distanced myself from many people :(
